00:03:31,830 --> 00:03:33,510
By getting that information, from our

111
00:03:33,510 --> 00:03:35,385
service desk, or our customer liaisons,

112
00:03:35,385 --> 00:03:37,440
we can get a lot of
the information we need

113
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,501
to build a good service
level management program.

114
00:03:39,501 --> 00:03:43,540
And then, afterwards, we want
to get customer feedback.

115
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:45,300
This can be something like a survey,

116
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:47,895
or looking at key business-related
measures and metrics.

